The protagonist, Naoya, is a first-year in high school. He asks out Saki, a girl he has been in love with, and she agrees to be his girlfriend. He's currently on cloud nine. But then, a beautiful girl named Nagisa comes up to Naoya one day and tells him that she wants to go out with him. Naoya feels himself wavering because Nagisa is such a good girl, and he comes to a decision! A new kind of romcom from a rather unexpected decision is about to begin!
(Source: Crunchyroll)
Action, Comedy, Drama, Psychological, Slice of Life, Supernatural

The story revolves around "Mob," a boy who will explode if his emotional capacity reaches 100%. This boy with psychic powers earned his nickname "Mob" because he does not stand out among other people. He keeps his psychic powers bottled up so he can live normally, but if his emotional level reaches 100, something will overwhelm his entire body.
(Source: Anime News Network)
Iinazuke ga Dekita to Omottara, Sono Iinazuke ga Gakkou de Yuumeina [Akuyaku Reijou] Dattan Dakedo, Dosureba Ii?

One Saturday morning, his father told him something shocking, “You have a fiancee."

Hiroyuki Higashikujo is a second-year high school boy. He goes between home and school without a girlfriend, but he is living a peaceful life without any complaints. Or, he was supposed to be, until all the marriage talk went on and on without regard to Hiroyuki...... and they were told that they are going to live together! His bride-to-be is a perfect young lady who goes to the same high school as Hiroyuki and she is smart, beautiful, and atheletic, too!

"I'm telling you, you don't have the right to refuse," she says with a face cold as absolute zero. This is the famous “villainess” of the school…!?

(Source: Dash Bunko, translated)
